snippet.title: Super Dark Deception | Official Intro
snippet.description:
Created to match the new Dark Deception intro cutscene, here is the new official intro video for Super Dark Deception! Wishlist Super Dark Deception on Steam! 
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2193720/Super_Dark_Deception/

Try the demo on Steam, Google Play, itch.io, and App Store!
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.GlowstickEntertainment.SuperDarkDeception&hl=en&gl=US
https://glowstickentertainment.itch.io/super-dark-deception
https://apps.apple.com/us/app/super-dark-deception-lite/id1494973595

Credits:
Composed by Major Bruno
Based on original music composed by Daniel Dombrowsky
2D Animation by elpichonart
Creative direction by Vincent Livings
Based on the 3D opening animation by Post Asylum & Element X.
